      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm looking at some Cessna manuals and trying to wrap my head around the pitot-static system. Can you explain exactly how a pitot tube works to measure airspeed and why it's such a critical component for flight safety?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
